atalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["frontend-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "pod_processes", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "trace_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时从8152.6ms激增至448054.7ms，延迟倍数高达55倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用链中频繁出现HTTP 500错误状态码，表明服务内部处理异常。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"GetProduct操作的平均耗时从10040.4ms增至11051.1ms，延迟显著增加。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ShipOrder操作的平均耗时从14434.9ms增至56198.7ms，延迟倍数接近4倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Charge操作的平均耗时从13865.8ms增至37817.0ms，延迟倍数接近3倍。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}", "log_analysis_findings": "基于日志分析结果，我已经识别出了系统异常的关键模式。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"FailedPrecondition\", \"Can't access cart storage\", \"rpc error\", \"cart storage\", \"Redis\", \"redis-cart:6379\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice 无法访问 Redis 存储，导致 FailedPrecondition 错误和 cart storage 访问失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error status code 'FailedPrecondition' with detail 'Can't access cart storage.' raised. 以及 Connecting to Redis: redis-cart:6379\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis 存储服务连接问题，导致 cartservice 无法访问购物车数据\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice 日志显示正在尝试连接 redis-cart:6379，但前端服务报告 Can't access cart storage\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析要点：\n\n1. **错误模式**：所有 frontend 实例都报告相同的错误模式 - `rpc error: code = FailedPrecondition desc = Can't access cart storage.`\n\n2. **根因服务**：cartservice 是问题的核心，它无法访问 Redis 存储，导致前端购物车功能失败\n\n3. **影响范围**：\n   - 所有 frontend 实例都受到影响（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n   - 所有 cartservice 实例都报告连接 Redis 的问题\n   - 错误在指定时间段内持续发生，出现频次较高\n\n4. **可能的根本原因**：\n   - Redis 服务（redis-cart）可能宕机或网络不可达\n   - Redis 连接配置问题\n   - 网络分区或 DNS 解析问题", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on my analysis of the metric data for the anomaly period from 2025-06-23T19:10:05Z to 2025-06-23T19:24:05Z, I've identified several significant anomalies. Here's my comprehensive analysis:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend service\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in server_error_ratio and error_ratio across all frontend pods, along with high rrt_max values\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend pods show error_ratio from 0.0 to 0.51-0.65 (median) and rrt_max p99 reaching 5-6 million (from ~250K normal)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High rrt_max and rrt values indicating performance degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 increased from 330K to 3.45M (1.65x change ratio), rrt p99 from 9.7K to 161K (1.77x change ratio)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Abnormal rrt_max and error_ratio patterns with pod_processes changes\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 changed from 83K to 6.2K (1.72x ratio), error_ratio p99 from 0.0 to 3.33, pod_processes showing process count variation\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice pods\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod_processes changes across all cartservice instances indicating potential restarts or process issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0, cartservice-1, cartservice-2 all show pod_processes p99 changing from 1.0 to 2.0 (0.67 ratio)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### Key Findings:\n\n1. **Frontend Service Issues**: All frontend pods (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2) show significant error rate increases from 0% to 51-65%, with extremely high maximum response times.\n\n2. **Performance Degradation**: Checkoutservice-1 exhibits severe performance issues with response times spiking dramatically.\n\n3. **Redis Service Anomaly**: redis-cart-0 shows unusual response time patterns and error rate changes, coupled with process count variations.\n\n4. **Pod Process Instability**: Multiple cartservice pods show process count changes, suggesting potential restarts or instability.\n\nThe most critical issues appear to be the frontend service error rates and the performance degradation in checkoutservice, which likely contributed to the overall system anomaly."}
